<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/8816> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #8816" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/7> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "p. 754, footnote 457" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/8324> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #8324" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "These men were witnesses to the resolutions of the Senate reported by Caelius to Cicero in Fam. 8.8.5-6." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7375> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7375" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Pr. by 58. The elderly L. Villius Annalis who was proscribed and killed in 43 is termed # by Appian (BC 4.18), but Appian must mean a man of praetorian rank, since his son, who was cognizant to the proceeding, was old enough to be a candidate for the quaestorship and was designated an aedile as a reward for his part in the matter (cf. Val. Max. 9.11.6). (TJC)\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5438> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5438" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "It is apparent that these senators are arranged in the order of seniority. L. Villius Annalis therefore held the praetorship before 57, and L. Ateius Capito and M. Eppius were ex- Quaestors in 51." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/5336> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #5336" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "See 51, Addendum." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/10451> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #10451" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/27> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Hinard suggests Villius was praetor II peregrinus in 43" .
